# Animation & Motion (Framer Motion)

## Principles

- Every animation must be **purposeful** — communicates state change, spatial relationship, or transition
- Never decorative: no bounce, overshoot, parallax, or 3D transforms
- Keep snappy: 150–300ms micro-interactions, 300–500ms page/panel transitions, never >500ms for in-page

## Easing

- Entrances: `ease-out`
- Exits: `ease-in`
- Morphs/color changes: `ease-in-out`

## Animation Specs

| Context | Animation | Duration |
|---|---|---|
| Page transitions | Fade + slide up ~8px | 300ms |
| Grid row expansion | Height expand + content fade-in | 250ms |
| Status change (Pass/Fail) | Color morph + brief pulse/glow | 200ms |
| Sidebar active indicator | Slide to selected item | 200ms ease-out |
| Modals/drawers | Scale 95%→100% + fade | 250ms |
| Toast notifications | Slide in from top-right | 300ms in, 200ms out |
| Data loading | Skeleton shimmer gradient sweep | Continuous |
| Hover states | Elevation lift + accent border glow | 150ms |
| Bulk select | Checkbox ripple + row highlight | 150ms |
| Chart rendering | Sequential bar/segment stagger | 50ms each, 400ms total |
| Drag-and-drop | Lifted shadow + placeholder ghost | Real-time |
| Expand/collapse chevron | Rotate 90° | 250ms |

## Framer Motion Patterns

```tsx
// Page transition wrapper
<motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 8 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: 'easeOut' }}>

// Modal/drawer entrance
<motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }} transition={{ duration: 0.25 }}>

// Status badge pulse on change
<motion.span animate={{ scale: [1, 1.15, 1] }} transition={{ duration: 0.2 }}>

// Staggered list (chart bars, cards)
<motion.div variants={container} initial="hidden" animate="visible">
  {items.map(item => <motion.div key={item.id} variants={child} />)}
</motion.div>
```
